<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Subscription Ended</title>
  <style>
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f6fa;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .body {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .body h2 {
      color: #4CAF50;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .body p {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #777777;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .body, .header {
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Subscription Ended</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.username %>,</h2>
      <p>
        We noticed that your subscription to <strong><%= @plan.plan_name %></strong> has ended. We hope you enjoyed our service!
      </p>
      <p>To continue enjoying uninterrupted access and exclusive features, please renew your subscription.</p>
      <a href="<%= root_url %>" class="cta-button">Renew Now</a>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Thank you,<br>Naukri App</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= Time.current.year %> Poplify India. All rights reserved.<br>
      Chandigarh, Panchkula | <a href="<%= root_url %>">Unsubscribe</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
